OL,3,CGovernment 'close' to fresh agreement
OL,4,Con NI's troubled past
OL,6,FSecretary of State Hilary Benn has
OL,7,Findicated the Government is "close" to
OL,8,Fa fresh agreement on how to deal with
OL,9,Fthe legacy of the Troubles.
OL,11,FMr Benn said a framework has been
OL,12,Fcreated following discussions with the
OL,13,FIrish Government including significant
OL,14,Freform of the Independent Commission
OL,15,Ffor Reconciliation and Information
OL,16,FRecovery (ICRIR) as well as
OL,17,Fprotections for army veterans.
