OL,3,CGovernment 'close' to fresh agreement
OL,4,Con NI's troubled past
OL,6,FAppearing before the Northern Ireland
OL,7,FAffairs Committee on Wednesday, the
OL,8,Fsecretary of state described dealing
OL,9,Fwith the past as the "unfinished
OL,10,Fbusiness" of the Belfast/Good Friday
OL,11,FAgreement from 1998.
OL,13,FMr Benn told MPs there had been "many
OL,14,Fattempts since", including the
OL,15,Fprevious government's controversial
OL,16,FLegacy Act, and reiterated the
OL,17,FGovernment's commitment to "repeal and
OL,18,Freplace" it.
