OL,6,FWhile some victims have called for the
OL,7,Fscrapping of the ICRIR, Mr Benn said
OL,8,Fhe is standing by his decision to
OL,9,Fretain it "for reasons of timing and
OL,10,Fpragmatism", but said it will be
OL,11,F"fundamentally reformed".
OL,13,F"I think we're close to being in a
OL,14,Fposition to announce an agreement," he
OL,15,Ftold MPs.
OL,17,FDeclining to say when draft
OL,18,Flegislation will be published, Mr Benn
OL,19,Fsaid he wants arrangements that will
OL,20,Fdeliver answers for families.
OL,26,@qD@KOUrD@KO]sD@AOUsD@XO]uD@AOUvD@cO]
