OL,6,FHe said the framework they have been
OL,7,Fworking on aims to build on the
OL,8,Fprinciples of the 2014 Stormont House
OL,9,FAgreement, and reflect the experience
OL,10,Fof Operation Kenova, which looked at
OL,11,Fthe activities of Stakeknife, thought
OL,12,Fto be the British Army's top agent
OL,13,Finside the Provisional IRA.
