OL,4,Con NI's troubled past
OL,6,F"That means a significantly reformed,
OL,7,Findependent and human rights compliant
OL,8,Fcommission (ICRIR), which gives
OL,9,Ffamilies the best chance of getting
OL,10,Fthose answers, investigations that are
OL,11,Fcapable of referring cases for
OL,12,Fpotential prosecution where there is
OL,13,Fevidence of criminality," he said.
