OL,3,CGovernment 'close' to fresh agreement
OL,4,Con NI's troubled past
OL,6,FHe described "significant reform" of
OL,7,Fthe ICRIR governance and powers,
OL,8,Fincluding independent oversight, the
OL,9,Fability to hold public hearings in
OL,10,Fsome cases, take sworn evidence, allow
OL,11,Ffamilies to have effective
OL,12,Frepresentation, and "much clearer
OL,13,Fconflict of interest arrangements".
OL,15,FHe also referred to "maximum
OL,16,Fdisclosure consistent with national
OL,17,Fsecurity" and the potential for a
OL,18,Fseparate information recovery body as
OL,19,Fwell as the resumption of a number of
OL,20,Finquests that have been prematurely
OL,21,Fhalted.
