OL,6,FMr Benn also said there will be
OL,7,Fprotections for veterans "who served
OL,8,Fwith great distinction to keep people
OL,9,Fsafe to ensure they're treated with
OL,10,Frespect in the legacy process".
OL,12,F"I've already said publicly, with
OL,13,Fmodern technology, there's no reason
OL,14,Fwhy veterans should have to travel to
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland to answer questions,"
OL,16,Fhe said.
OL,18,FHe added: "Those are the elements that
OL,19,FI've been discussing with the Irish
OL,20,FGovernment and we're looking to make
OL,21,Fprogress as soon as we possibly can.
